OL,3,CMan, 52, charged with murder of his
OL,4,Cmother after she was found stabbed
OL,6,FA 52 year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering his mother in south
OL,8,FDerbyshire, after she was found with
OL,9,Fstab wounds last month.
OL,11,FJoan Hardy, 72, was found dead at a
OL,12,Fproperty in The Crest, Linton, near
OL,13,FSwadlincote, at just after 2.30pm on
OL,14,F21 June.
OL,16,FPolice said the 72 year-old's son,
OL,17,FAdrian Hardy, of The Crest, has been
OL,18,Fcharged with her murder.
