OL,3,CMan, 52, charged with murder of his
OL,4,Cmother after she was found stabbed
OL,6,FMs Hardy's family are being supported
OL,7,Fby specialist officers from Derbyshire
OL,8,FPolice.
OL,10,FHardy has been remanded into custody
OL,11,Fand is due to appear before Southern
OL,12,FDerbyshire Magistrates' Court.
